":"Sara","meanings":["Variant of   Sarah .  This is the form used in the Greek of the New Testament (Hebrews 11:11)."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Sarah De Boville was born in 1250, in Gloucestershire, England, United Kingdom. She married John De Hotot about 1270, in Northamptonshire, England. They were the parents of at least 1 son. She died in England, United Kingdom."},"et":{"1250–":"1250–Surnud","1250–Male":"1250–Surnud","1265–Male":"1265–Surnud","1250–Female":"1250–Surnud","1265":"1265","1250":"1250","Abt 1270":"umbes 1270","England":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Northamptonshire, England":"Northamptonshire, England","Gloucestershire, England":"Gloucestershire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1250–":"1250–Kuollut","1250–Male":"1250–Kuollut","1265–Male":"1265–Kuollut","1250–Female":"1250–Kuollut","1265":"1265","1250":"1250","Abt 1270":"noin 1270","England":"Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Northamptonshire, England":"Northamptonshire, England","Gloucestershire, England":"Gloucestershire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1250–":"1250–Décédée","1250–Male":"1250–Décédé","1265–Male":"1265–Décédé","1250–Female":"1250–Décédée","1265":"1265","1250":"1250","Abt 1270":"environ 1270","England":"Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Northamptonshire, England":"Northamptonshire, Angleterre","Gloucestershire, England":"Gloucestershire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Sarah De Boville est née en 1250, à Gloucestershire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Elle a épousé John De Hotot environ 1270, à Northamptonshire, Angleterre. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fils. Elle est décédée à Angleterre, Royaume-Uni."},"de":{"1250–":"1250–Verstorben","1250–Male":"1250–Verstorben","1265–Male":"1265–Verstorben","1250–Female":"1250–Verstorben","1265":"1265","1250":"1250","Abt 1270":"um 1270","England":"England, United Kingdom","Northamptonshire, England":"Northamptonshire, England","Gloucestershire, England":"Gloucestershire, England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Sarah De Boville wurde 1250 in Gloucest